      "title": "Protests in Colombo Fort today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Representatives of many trade unions and civil organizations held a protest in front of the Colombo Fort railway station this afternoon (27) protesting against the attack on the Gallumuwadora struggle.",
        "The protestors demonstrated there by displaying placards with slogans like 'people's struggle, people's aspirations'."
      ],
